  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "1.2 知识产权律师行业",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34752519_8_5501-5560",
          "range": "5501-5560",
          "rangeStart": 5501,
          "rangeEnd": 5560,
          "markText": "通常，知识产权律师在处理案件的过程中较少接触到人生艰苦、人情冷暖，这对保持积极的人生态度和良好的工作热情可能大有裨益。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1766025982,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-12-18 10:46:22",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5501&rangeEnd=5560",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5501&rangeEnd=5560"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_8_5501-5560",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5501-5560",
      "markText": "通常，知识产权律师在处理案件的过程中较少接触到人生艰苦、人情冷暖，这对保持积极的人生态度和良好的工作热情可能大有裨益。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5501&rangeEnd=5560",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5501&rangeEnd=5560"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_8_2817-2877",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2817-2877",
      "markText": "虽然初入行业的律师需要时间去熬，但一旦熬出来，有自己独立的业务，做到合伙人级别，有自己的团队，就会开辟出属于自己的天地。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2817&rangeEnd=2877",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2817&rangeEnd=2877"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_7_2444-2594",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2444-2594",
      "markText": "研究表明，在2008—2012年这五年的专利权侵权案件中，采取“法定赔偿”的平均赔偿额只有8万元，通常只占到起诉人诉求额的1/3甚至更低。(4)",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2444&rangeEnd=2594",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2444&rangeEnd=2594"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_8_3100-3143",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3100-3143",
      "markText": "律师职业也只能实现中产阶层的收入，最多能实现富人阶层的梦想，成为顶级富豪是不太可能的。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3100&rangeEnd=3143",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3100&rangeEnd=3143"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_9_2262-2349",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2262-2349",
      "markText": "——前瞻思考：律师在接到工作任务时，应尽量向其上级律师或客户了解律师工作成果的最终用途，并在思考法律建议的过程中充分考虑各种可能出现的情形并提出相应的应对措施。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2262&rangeEnd=2349",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2262&rangeEnd=2349"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_7_4593-4613",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4593-4613",
      "markText": "我国未来的知识产权赔偿力度会进一步加强。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4593&rangeEnd=4613",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4593&rangeEnd=4613"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_8_6923-6996",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6923-6996",
      "markText": "正如上海“东方大律师”陶鑫良教授所言：“法律背面是商业，案件背后是利益。醉翁之意不在酒，讼争本质是商战。”归根结底，知识产权诉讼就是一种竞争方式。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6923&rangeEnd=6996",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6923&rangeEnd=6996"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_9_17151-17299",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "17151-17299",
      "markText": "下班时间到了，你的老师还没有走，最好在下班离开前问一下老师，还有没有什么事需要协助，而不是悄悄地溜走了。再如，和老师一起在会客室接待，如果客户的茶水快喝完了，要主动去续水，不要让老师提醒。 ",
      "totalCount": 44,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=17151&rangeEnd=17299",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=17151&rangeEnd=17299"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_5_2089-2117",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2089-2117",
      "markText": "需要在沟通中去管理客户的预期，进而获得客户的满意与信任。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2089&rangeEnd=2117",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2089&rangeEnd=2117"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_13_2401-2444",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "2401-2444",
      "markText": "第一是会议组织者的权威地位，第二是潜在客户对会议的关注程度，第三是会议发言的质量和水平",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2401&rangeEnd=2444",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2401&rangeEnd=2444"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_34_3845-3892",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "3845-3892",
      "markText": "而且吃饭谈事儿的客户可能并不打算付费，只是咨询一下，或者说，吃饭埋单的费用就是他支付的咨询费。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=3845&rangeEnd=3892",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=3845&rangeEnd=3892"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_5_1842-1940",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1842-1940",
      "markText": "其实法律检索的方向、步骤、目的和最终报告的形成，是很看得出一个律师的执业功底的，好的律师在每一个案件中会给案件类型画像，会给法官画像，会给对方律师画像，这样的律师还愁案件会败诉吗？还愁没有案源吗？",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1842&rangeEnd=1940",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1842&rangeEnd=1940"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_11_3388-3433",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3388-3433",
      "markText": "“世界上有两件事最难：一是把自己的思想装进别人的脑袋里；二是把别人的钱装进自己的口袋里。”",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3388&rangeEnd=3433",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3388&rangeEnd=3433"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_34_13201-13214",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "13201-13214",
      "markText": "不要过度评价客户的既往做法",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=13201&rangeEnd=13214",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=13201&rangeEnd=13214"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_5_1769-1842",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1769-1842",
      "markText": "人工智能和大数据在律师行业的应用，使得现在的检索大大区别于传统的法律检索，现有工具的使用节约了我们大量的时间，但是也减少了年轻律师思考锻炼的机会。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1769&rangeEnd=1842",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1769&rangeEnd=1842"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_7_8922-9022",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8922-9022",
      "markText": "2017年8月18日，全国首个互联网法院——杭州互联网法院挂牌成立。该院运用互联网技术，起诉、立案、送达、举证、开庭、裁判，每个环节全流程在线，在化解涉网纠纷、推动诉讼机制创新等方面都取得了显著成效。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8922&rangeEnd=9022",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8922&rangeEnd=9022"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_8_6248-6317",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6248-6317",
      "markText": "在知识产权领域，以诉讼对抗诉讼，从而达成某种目标，几乎是公开的秘密。当原告起诉被告时，被告可能反过来起诉原告，原告又可能开辟新的诉讼战场。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6248&rangeEnd=6317",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6248&rangeEnd=6317"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_8_7173-7192",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7173-7192",
      "markText": "更能培养和促进知识产权律师的商业思维。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7173&rangeEnd=7192",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7173&rangeEnd=7192"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_12_2057-2085",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "2057-2085",
      "markText": "除极个别情况外，陌生拜访和陌生电话是最差的律师营销方式。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2057&rangeEnd=2085",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2057&rangeEnd=2085"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34752519_15_6499-6544",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "6499-6544",
      "markText": "也不要轻易在文章里面批评某个公司，说不定哪天它就可能成为你的客户，因为，“互联网是有记忆的",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34752519&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=6499&rangeEnd=6544",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a4232ef072124807a42f66c?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=6499&rangeEnd=6544"
    }
  ],
